{"tid":1784572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"篤灰日本二人組木哥杏子，又重出江湖食人血饅頭","createTime":"2019-12-15T18:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T06:05:25.000Z","uid":269382,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2304d428a41fbf0a4d7531b9660cc3905decdd85","tid":1784572,"uid":269382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:11:39.000Z","msg":"早排因篤日本戰線文宣理惠小姐灰，比全城屌到七彩，最後在不否認下連fb都摺埋嘅木哥杏子，又重出江湖食人血饅頭，今次仲要食大茶飯，話係出年2月搞面白祭，話說呢個祭上幾年已經比參展商屌到撻皮，仲連啲炒散人工都走數。佢個面白祭fb已經開始有人招乎佢，但佢地一見屌留言就del，盡顯藍C風範，趁佢喺呢2個月要搵水魚sponsor，一定要打謝佢。<br />\n<br />\n面白祭fb：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/summerfeshk/photos/a.1421580321454231/2558596441085941/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsummerfeshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.1421580321454231%2F2558596441085941%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=c30e7ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/summerfeshk/photos/a.1421580321454231/2558596441085941/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n篤灰事件傳送門：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678258/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678258/page/1</a><br />\n熱血時報開節目屌柒佢：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/live/?v=966197477079594\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2Flive%2F%3Fv%3D966197477079594&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=e597e6e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/live/?v=966197477079594</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhS9sQX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhS9sQX.jpg&h=7269c361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mQvciZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mQvciZ.jpg&h=6dc509dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14e417ae4957b7c1883db2ce20f5e2d45fc30d2e","tid":1784572,"uid":125680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime